<h2 id="common-mistakes">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2>

<p>Avoiding common mistakes saves programs time, money, and frustration. Understanding these mistakes helps programs make informed decisions and avoid problems that can impact equipment protection, player experience, and long-term costs. Programs that learn from others' mistakes can optimize their baseball locker investments.</p>

